#: course/lesson-4-drawing-a-rectangle/lesson.bbcode:38
msgid "To turn 45 degrees to the right, you would write [code]turn_right(45)[/code]."
msgstr ""

#: course/lesson-4-drawing-a-rectangle/lesson.bbcode:39
msgid "If we call [code]turn_right(45)[/code], the turtle turns 45 degrees to the right before moving on to the next instruction."
