#: course/lesson-4-drawing-a-rectangle/lesson.bbcode:94
#. TRANSLATORS: Practice goal
msgid "Add the correct arguments to the functions [code]move_forward()[/code] and [code]turn_right()[/code] to draw a rectangle with a width of [code]200[/code] pixels, and a height of [code]120[/code] pixels."
